{"tid":843413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅首明年今日究竟係點唱？","createTime":"2018-10-01T06:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T09:32:57.000Z","uid":207149,"like":24,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b08c631c5e14ce4121d42b9673cd014af440c9","tid":843413,"uid":207149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"若這一刻我竟嚴重痴呆 根本不需要被愛<br />\n永遠在床上發（ ）餘生都不會再悲哀<br />\n <br />\n我由細到大都好鐘意Eason，差唔多佢首首歌都識背。<br />\n但早排發現明年今日嘅歌詞，竟然同我認知嘅唔同。<br />\n近年聽返所有版本，Eason都係將（呆）字唱做（夢）字，咁其實大家以前係聽到咩字。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：呆，由以前開始都係呆。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：自己聽錯話地硬，根本係夢。"},{"pid":"80648cf159e8113bc96580d31eb8b20e26d8328a","tid":843413,"uid":208726,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd720c1d2a622e37b4d6b1ead9f7aba043e0bade","tid":843413,"uid":28094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9 啦"},{"pid":"5c6e684fa340180d900636ecb29f126b895ec081","tid":843413,"uid":207149,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd720c1d2a622e37b4d6b1ead9f7aba043e0bade","tid":843413,"uid":28094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9 啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"我好記得係「永遠在床上發呆 餘生都不會再悲哀」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfda87e78d7315eb9bab4391bdd3f2bfd6c1df3","tid":843413,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"上一句咪有個呆字"},{"pid":"3e65ae0be6f4320b0a1b5208ca2e5d7531b7e6c3","tid":843413,"uid":35070,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:42:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用口唱，用聲帶發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\